sent.orig: Main component is financial system market dominant with bank dominant two sort model.
sent.trans: 金融制度主要分为市场主导型和银行主导型两种类型。

sent.orig: English and Miskito are the dominant languages, corrugated iron and wood the dominant building materials.
sent.trans: 英语和米斯基托与是当地的主要语言，弯曲褶皱的铁片和木材是当地主要的建材。

sent.orig: Genetics: Color mutation-The Hypo Boa is a Co-dominant or incomplete dominant trait.
sent.trans: 遗传学：彩色突变-该次宝儿是共同主导的或不完整的主要特征。

sent.orig: The dominant seventh chord pattern consists of the dominant, leading tone (leading note), supertonic and subdominant.
sent.trans: 属七和弦模式包括属音，主音，上主音和下属音。

sent.orig: Patterns can be horizontally dominant (window blinds) , vertically dominant (tree trunks) , or diagonal.
sent.trans: 能横向统治（窗口百叶窗）、垂直统治（树干），或斜。
